&lt;h2 id=&#34;frame-search:6979efd3b17fef3a3f6df080ae321b47&#34;&gt;Frame Search&lt;/h2&gt;


&lt;figure &gt;
    
        &lt;img src=&#34;http://rayrshah.github.io/work/images/frames/lowy-sm.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;The final tool with search contained within the sidebar&#34; /&gt;
    
    
